  "At 6.0%: PMT ≈ $1,799, total = $647,500. At 7.5%: PMT ≈ $2,098, total = $755,200. Difference ≈ $107,700. A good credit score saves over $100,000 on a single mortgage — making credit building one of the highest-ROI financial activities.": "占6.0%:PMT = 1,799美元,总额= 647,500美元,占7.5%:PMT = 2,098美元,总额= 755,200美元,差额 = 107,700美元,一个好的信用分数在一次抵押贷款上节省了10万美元以上,使信贷建设成为国际救济组织最高金融活动之一。",
  "A 28-year-old earns $55,000, saves 15% ($8,250/year) in a 401(k) with a 4% employer match ($2,200/year). Total $10,450/year at 8% for 37 years to age 65 will grow to approximately:": "一个28岁的孩子收入为55 000美元,在401(k)中节省了15%(每年8 250美元),雇主比额为4%(每年2 200美元)。",
